# GET /api/v1/page/content/{lang}/{id}

+ Parameters

    + id: `41f70225-9231-4caa-93a4-db025486ba42` (uuid)
        The id of content.

    + lang: en (string)
        The language localization of content.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

